{"rightSidebarLinks":[{"id":"decorators","title":"decorators","subLink":null},{"id":"http","title":"http","subLink":[]},{"id":"xhrfilter","title":"xhrFilter","subLink":[]},{"id":"inmemory","title":"inMemory","subLink":[]}],"title":"Decorators","description":"","validatorType":"validators","validationTypeTitle":"Validators","type":"simple","category":"http","subCategory":"","linkTitle":"decorators","tabArray":{},"innerHtml":null,"htmlContent":"<div class=\"title-bar\"><p>While using Http methods, there are some scenarios when you have to set the config like to append any api path after the main path or if you want to set hostKey, you can set it through decorators.</p></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'http'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>http<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/http/decorators/validators#http'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >If you want to set the hostKey and path for your server side api, you can do it with the help of <span class='highlighted'>@http</span> decorator of <span class='highlighted'>RxHttp</span>.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"app-decorators-http\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'xhrfilter'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>xhrFilter<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/http/decorators/validators#xhrfilter'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >If you want to set config object including any arguments or model to pass while making XHR calls (i.e. using XMLHttpRequest), you can do it with the help of <span class='highlighted'>@xhrFilter</span> decorator of <span class='highlighted'>RxHttp</span>.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"app-decorators-xhrFilter\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'inmemory'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>inMemory<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/http/decorators/validators#inmemory'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"app-decorators-inMemory\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n"}